summary: Level 1 Nord - Vienna (Based on Taylor Swift)
descriptionHtml:
This is Vienna - A Female Nord
She is loosely Based on \"Taylor Swift\"
Save gave right after beginning cave.

You will need this mods to get the same result as screenshots:

No More Blocky Faces
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=30

Detailed Faces
http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=26

Hope you enjoy her as much as I have ;)
Feel free to share or modify, credits are always appreciated :)
Comments are appreciated!
